ATTRIBUTION NOTICE:
This project (Midnight Chameleon) is a fork and revival of the original 
Midnight Lizard extension created by Pavel Agarkov. The original project 
is available at: https://github.com/Midnight-Lizard/Midnight-Lizard

This fork was created to:
- Migrate the extension to Manifest V3
- Continue maintenance and development
- Fix compatibility issues with modern browsers

We are grateful to Pavel Agarkov for creating the original extension and 
releasing it under the MIT license, which enables this community revival.
